name: Shibblack inu
description: SHIBBLACK INU aims to offer the crypto community several services: a Farm-to-Earn virtual farmland, an NFT marketplace and a DAO. A vision similar to Kimbal Musk to radically improve the food supply chain efficiency, nutrition value, making indoor growing cheaper and more reliable, SHIBBLACK INU is poised to gain huge market share in virtual farming.
